> Does this mean we can remove all of the -- from the man page markdown?

@rhatdan do you mean the `\-\-`? (github markdown might have mangled your post there)

If so, yes, those can be converted back to plain `--` in the markdown. I think that might also require undoing this change to [hack/xref-helpmsgs-manpages](https://github.com/containers/podman/commit/bc48211924bd8f88263149f8b5d047a52f8d1733#diff-52a2253a031fa57a166303ddeefed8695b406163cce8708b3476ea1dda436361) in bc48211
